WE got 10 lucky packages for the first 10 customers. If you like our product, don't hesitate now. Only takes you $79 to get a Dyson-quality hairdryer plus a hand dryer? Why Wait?


 
​Do you spend too much time drying your hair with a super noisy hairdryer and always trouble storing the hairdryer after use?Do you wanna reduce tissue usage to protect the planet? Do you like to save your time washing your towel every week and have better hand care?We have found our solution-CIVISOLO All-in-one Hair & Hand Dryer for you. Check this out!Convenient, dry your hair in 3 mins, high negative ions, the CIVISOLO hairdryer is the smart option for your hair dry without harming your hair.The perfect combination of straight air duct and powerful brushless motor brings the strong wind up to 18-18.5m/s. The wind pressure is up to 100g and gets your hair and hands dry quicker. Most of the hairdryers can only produce 6-7m/s air flow.A brushless motor up to 110,000RPM brings stronger airflow. Installed with capacitors reduce the noise and maintain a long motor life. CIVISOLO Unidryer brings a quiet and fast-drying experience.The installed anion launcher release over 300W high negative ions. It will reduce the static and smooth the hair when blowing your hair. It is designed to prevent irritable and bifurcated hair. Healthy hair can reflect the sunlight. Installed with the heat control chip, the CIVISOLO Unidryer controls the temperature of airflow to prevent hair damage caused by overheat airflow. In one word, we are looking for a healthy and efficient hair drying experience.According to new research from the University College London, you should be looking at washing your hands around 6-10 times a day – with the findings suggesting that washing on such a regular basis will help lower your chances of contracting coronavirus. We hope CIVISOLO can bring you a great hair dry experience. At the same time, we hope it can be your health guard. Meanwhile, together we can protect our planet starting by using less tissue today. This is why we need your support CIVISOLO-A hand dryer for your everyday use.When you place the hairdryer back in the storage box, it will turn into a hand dryer.No extra power supply needed and the fashion design of our hand dryer will upgrade your bathroom immediately.With the installed infrared sensor and smart chip, the hand dryer is 100% automatic. The automation better product quality, improved safety, and accuracy. More importantly, it helps maintain a longer life of the hand dryer.Since the Covid-19 outbreak, people wash hands more often and it became the first important thing to do when home. The number of used tissue has been increasing and more trees have been cut. People also worry about the health problem caused by using a towel full of bacterias. Now we have found the best solution for you.According to the study of Statista and our test data, you can save at least $178.3 a year per family. Also, you save at least 1/5 of the big tree being cut, it is the combination of money-saving and contribution to the environment.In a study, Charles Gerba, a microbiologist at, University of Arizona, found 90 percent of bathroom towels to have been contaminated with coliform bacteria while 14 percent of them were found to carry E Coli. Many of us may unknowingly use such towels but in the process, the bacteria rubs on the body, which is harmful. To avoid that, you have to wash your towel twice a week with hot water and change it every 3 months. It will cost you more time and money to keep your towel clean than using a hand dryer.A family with 4 members uses 26.8lbs of tissues every year (dry hand 5 times a day)and about 1/5 tree is cut down for tissue making. It might look like a small number. But do you know over 27,000 trees are cut down every day for tissue making? Every year over 9,855,000 trees are cut down for tissue making. Your first step of replacing tissue with a hand dryer will be part of the big step of protecting our planet.The brushless motor brings strong wind and cooperates with the high-power heat to guide your hair drying. It is not tight. Through infrared induction, magnetic switch, and other components, it can quickly turn into a Pro hand dryer.We design 3 temperature modes and 2 wind modes. The accurate heat system protects your hair from overheat. Meanwhile, three million negative ions would bring you a more enjoyable hair care experience. By connecting the hairdryer, there is no extra power needed for the hand dryer. It improves safety and saves your electricity when you are not using the hand dryer.We have designed a smarter air duct for you. It reduces running costs by up to 50% compared to a traditional hand dryer and dries your hands in 15 seconds. The wide air duct design also prevents your hands from getting heat at one point. That will protect your hand skin and brings better hand care. Starts working when detecting your hands by infrared sensor and stops when your hands are left. It is efficient and saves you electricity fees.The hermetic design of the hand dryer ensures no water can get into the machine even in the wet bathroom with moisture. The cable is also waterproof to ensure user safety.The security design is designed for the situation that it is not in use properly. When the cover is not 100% closed and hermetic, the hand dryer would cut down the electricity to protect you. It will guarantee that no water can get into the system at any time.The modern design of our CIVISOLO Unidryer matches with different home styles no matter it is modern, vintage, or ape Cod.Light and small the CIVISOLO Unidryer is the perfect hairdryer you can travel with. It would only take a small corner of your suitcase and it is only 320g. Bringing it with you can make sure your hair looks perfect anywhere, anytime.Light and small the CIVISOLO Unidryer is the perfect hairdryer you can travel with. It would only take a small corner of your suitcase and it is only 320g. Bringing it with you can make sure your hair looks perfect anywhere, anytime.Wind level test Up to 18-18.6m/s. Most of the top brands(Price is over $300) reach 18.WaterProof TestWe have done over waterproof tests in over 3 different bathroom types and over 1000 waterproof tests from 4 different angles to ensure the use safety of the hand dryer.Yep，you are right. Installing our unidryer is not that hard. No SCREWS and GLUE needed. Just stick the backing on any tile or glass surface for a mess-free installation in seconds. We already got everything you need in the box. You can stick the backing on any tiles, glass, cabinets.CIVISOLO unidryer uses a Type A plug that is commonly used in the US, Canada, China. An adapter would be required for countries that use a different type of outlet. It doesn’t matter in what part of the world you live in, CIVISOLO will definitely work.2 years ago it started with the question of our colleague: why the hand dryer in our office building is ugly and not comfy to use it. At the first beginning, we were thinking to create a cool handler and then we came up with the idea of creating a unit dryer that can also help our colleagues to dry their hair in the office building sometimes when raining. We can't stop after that. we then have lots of brainstorming after that. We built up a project team and started working on this project. What we hope is to create a uni dryer that can let our customers enjoy hair drying and protect the planet more by using fewer tissues.CIVISOLO is a home tech gadget brand that aims to bring better, healthier, more eco-friendly life quality to our customers. With a team of many experts from Alibaba and Oracle, the team got many awards such as the German RedDot award and owns 50 patents of different home tech products. We are still improving and creating based on more new customer demands. In one word, CIVISOLO wants to be the friend of your comfy home.We have started our first mass production on the 27th of May. Before that, we have done QA tests and safety tests. We aim to deliver the quality our customers are happy with. We hope you will be excited and enjoy using it when you get our CIVISOLO Unidryer.CIVISOLO Unidryer has got the FCC Certification. We are strict with every product we produce no matter in quality or safety.

